{"tid":781322,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"嘴突而箍牙嘅請入","createTime":"2018-08-15T22:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T15:19:04.000Z","uid":189300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f36a7bf1da541e15f291f0e3b769e6185e032c39","tid":781322,"uid":189300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:09:05.000Z","msg":"身為嘴突嘅人點想有一日係影到一張正常嘅側面相<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過嘴突都有好多原因 小至mok牙落骨釘上箍就收得翻入去 大至可能要做手術先可以搞得掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然錢都係最致命嘅原因 令好多人都心動但行動唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家可以係度留低自己嘅經歷 無論你已經做完定啱啱先開始做呢方面嘅research都好 一齊分享下 等更多人更加有信心去了解多少少自己可以點樣解決 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">例如有咩醫生係呢方面case比較有經驗 自己應該大概預幾多budget 等等。。。 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>集思廣益去正視問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  終有一日會影到側面相<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0ec2158dff153b6ef06308df14af3a6bc177ab94","tid":781322,"uid":83033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T23:07:38.000Z","msg":"雖然同你既煩惱唔關事<br />\n不過我想講有啲人會中意嘴突既人<br />\n例如我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721873032effcd5d23c06ff89ae3333568f2007b","tid":781322,"uid":18899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T23:12:34.000Z","msg":"比多少少睇專科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e51f4baf3717fb72afec52ebd9752aa1992400","tid":781322,"uid":189300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ec2158dff153b6ef06308df14af3a6bc177ab94","tid":781322,"uid":83033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T23:07:38.000Z","msg":"雖然同你既煩惱唔關事<br />\n不過我想講有啲人會中意嘴突既人<